michael.name: St. Michael
michael.shortDescription: Leader of the heavenly armies and protector of the faithful.
michael.descriptionEn: St. Michael is the leader of the heavenly armies and protector of the faithful.
michael.descriptionAm: ቅዱስ ሚካኤል የሰማይ ሰራዊት አለቃ ነው፣ ለምእመናን አጋእ እና ተከላካይ ይሆናል።
